# Testing Rules

## Philosophy

All new functionality must include tests.

Required coverage:


graph queries
signal scoring
entity resolution
retrieval logic


## Test Types

Use:

- unit tests
- integration tests
- pipeline tests

## Example


describe("Signal scoring", () => {
it("should assign higher score to trusted sources", () => {
...
})
})


## Execution Timing

Tests must run:


before merge
before release
after ingestion pipeline updates


CI must block merges when tests fail.